  "detailed_description": "Test your skills with this fast-paced arcade game. Put the falling shapes into their right place as fast as you can, but be careful: more shapes will fall down while the level goes on... Try to get first place in the world rank leaderboard!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 15 different levels to play<br></li><li> Each shape has its own physics!<br></li><li> Random power-ups will drop down to help you! catch them all!<br></li><li> Unlock many different cursors to push the shapes better!<br></li><li> Steam Leaderboard</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Each shape goes into the correct space</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1177820/extras/dcec10c26c53e50c24efea81647eb285.poster.avif?t=1771233093\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1177820/extras/dcec10c26c53e50c24efea81647eb285.webm?t=1771233093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1177820/extras/dcec10c26c53e50c24efea81647eb285.mp4?t=1771233093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Can you catch that annoying little man laughing?</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1177820/extras/ea8249b15f0c1080246db5620a0e884f.poster.avif?t=1771233093\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1177820/extras/ea8249b15f0c1080246db5620a0e884f.webm?t=1771233093\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1177820/extras/ea8249b15f0c1080246db5620a0e884f.mp4?t=1771233093\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >There are also some bonus like Extra Time!<